<h1> Accurate scaled data </h1>
<h2> The scalers:</h2>
<h3><ul><A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/inger.html">Inger</a> 
 <A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/Kurt.html">Kurt</a>
 <A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/Ove.html">Owe</a> 
 <A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/Robert.html">Robert</a> 
</ul><h4>
accurate scaled ionograms are here as ascii files with the names:styy/styymm.fil (e.g. ly96/ly9601.fil)
<h1>
<A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki91.html">ki91</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki92.html">ki92</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki93.html">ki93</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki94.html">ki94</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki95.html">ki95</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ki96.html">ki96</A>
<h1>
<A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly91.html">ly91</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly92.html">ly92</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly93.html">ly93</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly94.html">ly94</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly95.html">ly95</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/ly96.html">ly96</A>
<h1>
<A HREF="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/up91.html">up91</a>
<a href="http://www.irf.se/~ionogram/ionogram/scaledData/up92.html">up92</a>
