<h2> Projects at the Department of Forest and Water Management </h2> <HR>
<h3> <a href="projects.html">Projects at the Laboratory of Hydrology and Water Management  </a></h3>
An overview of the main projects at LHWM. Available as a <a href="projects.html">clickable map </a> or as <a href="projectsold.html">text with some images. </a><HR>

<h3> <a href="http://taoren.rug.ac.be/sigpac"> SIGPAC </a> </h3>
Forest monitoring by satellite and integrated watershed management in Costa Rica. (Spanish and English version available)<HR>
