<H3><A HREF=/home.html><IMG SRC="/pictures/smallfront.gif" WIDTH="100" HEIGHT="40"></A></H3> 
<h1> STUDENTS SERVICE </h1>
Dear, <p>
This part of the home page of the Laboratory of Hydrology and Water Management will be
setup to allow students to get more involved with our lab. I am thinking to announce thru this page
hot topics about our courses, time shedules, possible thesis proposals, maybe job announcements or
trainee proposals. I know that students are getting more and more involved into the huge internet world.
 Of course none of the announcements here are really official but it allows the students to keep in touch.
I am not really intending to do this if there is no request from students. Therefore I suggest following;
mail to me (Bart.Cosyn@rug.ac.be) and leave me your E-mail address. In this way I can get an idea about the 
number of interested students!
<p>
I  really hope this becomes succes and than for sure I am willing to put some time in these anouncements.
<HR>
<h3>You want to create your own homepage? </h3>
The <a href="http://www.rug.ac.be/arc/index.html">Academic Computing Center </a> of the University Gent gives, all people able to access the server of the University, the possibility to create
their own home page on <a href="http://studwww.rug.ac.be"> eduserv.rug.ac.be </a> or allserv.rug.ac.be (staff members only). You will find the
 needed info on the site itself.
<HR>
<h3> <a href="/stud/thesisprop.html"> Thesis Proposals </a> </h3>  <HR>
<h3> <a href="ftp://darling.rug.ac.be/pub/pub/virus"> Virus scanners  </a> 
<IMG SRC="/gif/new.gif" ALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="29" HEIGHT="18" SGI_FULLPATH="/tmp_mnt/hosts/taoren/www/gif/new.gif"> 
</H3>
Protect your diskets and your computer against virus violation. Download the newest Mcafee and Thunderbyte antivirus scanners (w95,w3.1,dos) from our ftp site. (latest version feb 1996). <HR>
<H3> <a href="http://studwww.rug.ac.be/~avgasse/VLK/index.html"> VLK home page </a>
<IMG SRC="/gif/new.gif" ALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="29" HEIGHT="18" SGI_FULLPATH="/tmp_mnt/hosts/taoren/www/gif/new.gif"> 
</H3>
A link to the VLK (students organisation of the faculty). 
