<H2><A NAME="SECTION00032000000000000000">CRS4 in the EC Project</A></H2>
<P>
One of the tasks of CRS4 in the project will be to develop
an overall ``systems environment'' for the project.
The key components of this environment are:
<OL><LI>  A geographic information system (GIS), to process and manipulate
       site-specific raster, vector, and point data;<LI>  A data management system,
       to organize as efficiently as possible both the data and
       information about the data;<LI>  A data visualization system, for analysis and visualization
       of large datasets in a fast and user-friendly way;<LI>  An information retrieval system, for access and sharing of
       information between all members and sites involved in the project.
</OL><BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Bart Cosyn <BR>
Thu Jul 25 13:19:15 MDT 1996</I>
