<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Orthofotomaps</TITLE>
<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Orthofotomaps">
<META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="paper">
<META NAME="resource-type" CONTENT="document">
<META NAME="distribution" CONTENT="global">
<LINK REL=STYLESHEET HREF="paper.css">
</HEAD>
<BODY LANG="EN">
 <A NAME="tex2html341" HREF="node16.html"><IMG WIDTH=37 HEIGHT=24 ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="next" SRC="http://taoren.rug.ac.be/lat2html/next_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME="tex2html339" HREF="node12.html"><IMG WIDTH=26 HEIGHT=24 ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="up" SRC="http://taoren.rug.ac.be/lat2html/up_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME="tex2html333" HREF="node14.html"><IMG WIDTH=63 HEIGHT=24 ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="previous" SRC="http://taoren.rug.ac.be/lat2html/previous_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME="tex2html343" HREF="node1.html"><IMG WIDTH=65 HEIGHT=24 ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="contents" SRC="http://taoren.rug.ac.be/lat2html/contents_motif.gif"></A>  <BR>
<B> Next:</B> <A NAME="tex2html342" HREF="node16.html">Soil Maps and Soil </A>
<B>Up:</B> <A NAME="tex2html340" HREF="node12.html">Permanent Data of the </A>
<B> Previous:</B> <A NAME="tex2html334" HREF="node14.html">Topographic Maps</A>
<BR> <P>
<H3><A NAME="SECTION00042300000000000000">Orthofotomaps</A></H3>
<P>
At LHWM 3 RGB (red-green-blue) 24-bit orthofotomaps are 
available for the Passemare and Sassegem subcatchments.
These orthofotomaps are airborne photos taken by
EUROSENSE N.V. in 1990. 
Prints of the orthofotomaps are available on a scale of 1:10000 at LHWM.
These orthofotoplans are a useful visual tool for checking the
accuracy of data positioning and digitalization. The goal is to
use these images to distinguish individual fields on the 
subcatchments and for positioning of the field
scale ground truth data collection points.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Bart Cosyn <BR>
Thu Jul 25 13:19:15 MDT 1996</I>
