<H3><A NAME="SECTION00054200000000000000">Ground Truth Campaigns 1994</A></H3>
<P>
An overview of the data collected during the various campaigns is given below. 
Surface roughness is also measured during all campaigns.
<DL ><DT><STRONG>April 6</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> TDR: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm in the Sassegem subcatchment<LI> pF-rings (soil core samples to determine  <IMG WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=18 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="tex2html_wrap_inline2855" SRC="img19.gif"  > )
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> ERS-1
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> Weather station (questionable)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>April 9</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> TDR: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm in the Passemare subcatchment<LI> pF-rings
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> ERS-1<LI> EMAC
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> Weather station (questionable)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>April 10</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem subcatchment<LI> TDR: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm in the Passemare subcatchment<LI> pF-rings
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> SIR-C/X-SAR (no images yet)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> Weather station (questionable)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>April 11</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> TDR: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm in the Passemare subcatchment<LI> pF-rings
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> SIR-C/X-SAR
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> Weather station (questionable)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>June 16</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm on several fields of the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> pF-rings (average value of  <IMG WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=18 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="tex2html_wrap_inline2855" SRC="img19.gif"  >  for 0-10&nbsp;cm)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> ERS-1
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 1 Bowen ratio station (University of Gent)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>June 30</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> TDR: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm in the Passemare subcatchment
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> EMAC (no images yet)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 1 Bowen ratio station (University of Gent)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>August 19</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm, 5-10&nbsp;cm, and 10-20&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments<LI> pF-rings ( <IMG WIDTH=16 HEIGHT=18 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="tex2html_wrap_inline2855" SRC="img19.gif"  >  for 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> EMAC (no images yet)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> 1 eddy correlation station (University of Basel)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>August 29</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm on several fields of the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> ERS-1
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> 1 eddy correlation station (University of Basel)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>September 10 (to be verified)</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm, 5-10&nbsp;cm, and 10-20&nbsp;cm 
          on several fields of the Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> J-ERS-1 (no images yet)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> 1 eddy correlation station (University of Basel)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>October 1 (to be verified)</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Passemare subcatchment
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> SIR-C/X-SAR (no images yet)
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Time dependent data</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> 2 Bowen ratio stations (Universities of Gent and Basel)<LI> 1 eddy correlation station (University of Basel)<LI> Weather station (not logging)<LI> Discharges
    </UL> 
 </DL>
<P>
<DT><STRONG>October 2 (to be verified)</STRONG>
<DD> 
  <DL ><DT><STRONG>Soil moisture measurements</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> Gravimetric: 0-5&nbsp;cm and 5-10&nbsp;cm along transects in the 
          Sassegem and Passemare subcatchments
    </UL>
  <DT><STRONG>Remote sensing</STRONG>
<DD> 
    <UL><LI> SIR-C/X-SAR (no images yet)
    </UL>
