<H2><A NAME="SECTION00081000000000000000">Definition of the ``Location'' for the Zwalm Catchment</A></H2>
<P>
The Zwalm catchment is situated southeast of Gent.
The area of the catchment is approximately 114 km <IMG WIDTH=6 HEIGHT=9 ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="tex2html_wrap_inline2775" SRC="img5.gif"  > .
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html795" HREF="node54.html#SECTION00081100000000000000">UTM Coordinates</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html796" HREF="node55.html#SECTION00081200000000000000">Row and Column Setup</A>
<LI> <A NAME="tex2html797" HREF="node56.html#SECTION00081300000000000000">Lambert Coordinates</A>
</UL>
<BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Bart Cosyn <BR>
Thu Jul 25 13:19:15 MDT 1996</I>
