<BODY VLINK="#ff0000" LINK="#ffff00" BGCOLOR="#42426f" TEXT="#ffffff">
<h1> Thesis Proposals </h1>
To know more about thesis proposals please contact <a href="/~peter">
Dr. ir. P. Troch </a>.
We have no real limitations on subjects as long as it concerns water, water management, hydrology, irrigation and so on.
<h2>Possible keywords:</h2>
Hydrologic modelling, remote sensing in hydrology, GIS in hydrology, irrigation, drainage,
evapotranspiration modelling, measuring technology, precipitation modelling, ground water modelling,
water quality modelling, geothermal sources in Tunisia and much more.
<h2> <a href="thtun.html">Thesis in Tunisia </h2></a>

