<H3><A NAME="SECTION00073100000000000000">Reference Systems</A></H3>
<P>
The reference system in Belgium has the following characteristics&nbsp;[<A HREF="node63.html#twem"><EM>Van&nbsp;Twembeke, </EM><EM>Van&nbsp;Twembeke</EM><EM>
  1994</EM></A>]:
<DL ><DT><STRONG>Ellipsoid</STRONG>
<DD>
  Hayford; <I>a</I> = 6378388&nbsp;m, <I>e</I> = 0.0818541
<P>
  <DT><STRONG>Orientation</STRONG>
<DD> 
  At the point  <IMG WIDTH=331 HEIGHT=30 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="tex2html_wrap_inline2953" SRC="img52.gif"  >  
  the astronomic coordinates coincide with the geodetic coordinates.
<P>
 </DL><BR> <HR>
