<H3><A NAME="SECTION00081300000000000000">Lambert Coordinates</A></H3>
<P>
The choice between Lambert and UTM coordinates has been a
matter of some discussion. Any processing from one
projection system to another introduces errors. As there 
will probably not be an overall GIS setup for all the test
sites in the EC project together, it is perhaps best 
to choose the projection system most appropriate for each 
individual site (for instance, the
projection currently in use by the different partners),
and to define a common projection for purposes of file transfer
and data management, for instance:
north:      215100 <BR> 
south:      70000 <BR> 
east:       200000 <BR> 
west:       80000 <BR> 
cols:       12000 <BR> 
rows:       14510 <BR> 
e-w resol:  10 <BR> 
n-s resol:  10
<BR> <HR>
<P><ADDRESS>
<I>Bart Cosyn <BR>
Thu Jul 25 13:19:15 MDT 1996</I>
