<H3><A NAME="SECTION00083100000000000000">ZWALMlamb</A></H3>
<P>
Mapset IMAGES:
<PRE>3d.view:              views for use in SG3d and d.3d
dtm:                  a 3dview of the dem
ortho.dtm:            orthogonal view of the dem

raster files:
060494v.raw:          ERS-1 image 6 April (not rescaled)
090494v.raw:          ERS-1 image 9 April (not rescaled) 
april:                red Green composite april images (sample)
060494v.raw.res:      255 rescaled image of 6 April
090494v.raw.res:      255 rescaled image of 9 April

vectorfiles:
swathss:              midswath line EMAC April 
trans.0494:           transect points campaign April

groups:
april:                images of 6 and 9 April (rescaled)  
april.raw:            images of 6 and 9 April (raw data) 
toUTM:                DEM related group for conversion

icons:
crelectors.april:     icon for corner reflectors at EMAC/SIR-C April 
soilmois.trans:       icon for soil moisture sampling points April
trans.0494:           icon for transect positioning April

labels:
crelectors.april:     labels for corner reflectors at EMAC/SIR-C April
midswathEMAC:         labels for reference midswath points April

sites:
crelectors.april:     site list corner reflectors at EMAC/SIR-C April
midswathEMAC:         site list reference midswath points April
soilmois.trans:       data file soil moisture sample (only accessible 
                      thru d.trans shells)
trans.0494:           site list transect positioning April</PRE>
<P>
Mapset PERMANENT:
<PRE>Raster data:
zwalm30.dem.res:      rescaled DEM (grid 30) to intervals of 10 m 
                      in height
zwalmnet.dig:         network of channels derived from digitized vectors
zwalmtop.usgs:        topindex for each pixel derived from 30 m DEM
topomap1.raw:         raster topo map of north of catchment (example) 
zwalm30dem.usgs:      DEM corrected of digitalization errors and pits 
                      (USGS derived)
zwalmnet.usgs:        network derived thru USGS programs and tools
zwalm30.dem:          original DEM (30 m grid)
zwalmmask.dig:        mask file Zwalm derived from digitized vector
zwalmslop.usgs:       slopes calculated thru USGS tools
zwalm30.dem.a2:       adapted DEM in order to get a better fit of the 
                      mask file derived by USGS software.
zwalmmask.usgs:       mask file derived from unadapted DEM
zwalmsub.dig:         subcatchments derived from digitized vectors

vectors:
zwalm30.cont:         contourlines of DEM (interval 20 meters)
zwalmdiv.dig:         watershed of the Zwalm digitized
zwalmnetw.dig:        network of channels digitized
zwalmsub.dig:         subcatchments digitized

icons:
stations:             icon for stations of monitoring network 
                      (cfr. shell stations)

labels:
stations:             labels for stations of monitoring network 
                      (cfr. shell stations)

sites:
station:              sitelist for stations of monitoring network 
                      (cfr. shell stations)

windows:
dem:                  window fitting the complete DEM
pass:                 window containing Passemare catchment
sass:                 window containing Sassegem catchment</PRE>
<P>
