<H4><A NAME="SECTION00083310000000000000">Acknowledgments.</A></H4>
<P>
This work could only be done thanks to the support of all my colleagues at
CRS4 and the collaborators of the Laboratory of Hydrology and Water
Management at the University of Gent.
In particular I would like to thank Claudio Paniconi who invited me to
work at CRS4 during the period Oct/94-Jan/95
and Prof. Dr. ir. F. De Troch and Peter Troch who supported me
during last two years in Gent. Last but not least I thank
Bob Su and Lieven Nachtergale for the data retrieval, Andrea Giacomelli for
the introductions in GRASS and all the colleagues in the project 
and at CRS4.  -  ir. Bart Cosyn
