	<h2>New Building Construction Log</h2>

This construction log is brought to you by Barnes Construction, in partnership with Turner Construction.  The Tech also thanks Tarlton Property Managemement for the use of their premises.  Use the controls below to see images, video, and
commentary for various dates throughout the construction process.

<p>

