<head>
<title>Our Mission</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width=100%>

<tr>
<td align=left valign=bottom>
<a href="/"><img src="/anims/techlogospintech.gif" border=0 alt="" align=middle></a></td>
<td width=75%>
<a href="http://www.thetech.org/hyper"><img src="/ads/htvisit.gif" width=397 height=86 border=0 alt="This space for rent.  Contact Mike Rose (mrose@thetech.org) for more info." align=middle></a>

