<td valign=top width=75%>

<h2>Exhibits at The Tech</h2>

The Tech includes these exhibits, and many others described in various <a href="/news">press releases</a>.  Come visit The Tech to see them for yourself, or take a peek here first.
<p>

<a href="/exhibits/exhibit_hall.html"><img src="/gifs/exhibits/exhibit_hall-8.gif" alt=""></a>
<p><a href="/exhibits/exhibit_hall.html">The Tech's Exhibit Hall</a> features exhibits in several major areas:<p>
<h2><a href="/exhibits/bicycles/">Bicycles</a></h2>
<p><a href="/exhibits/bicycles/"><img src="/gifs/exhibits/bicycles-8.gif" alt=""></a>
