<td valign=top width=75%>
<h2>Educational Programs for Teachers and Students</h2>
The Tech's education programs include hands-on labs for
students (contact <a href="mailto:barbaras@thetech.org">barbaras@thetech.org</a>) and workshops (contact <a href="mailto:tdirks@thetech.org">tdirks@thetech.org</a>) and other resources for teachers.

<p>

<a href="/wov"><img src="http://media.thetech.org/edu/wovicon.GIF" align=right border=0 alt="" hspace=15></a>
<font size="-1"><b>WOMEN OF VISION FOR THE TECH</b></font><p>
The <a href="/wov">Women of Vision for The Tech</a> serves as a
resource for encouraging girls to continue math and
science studies and consider careers in technical fields.
<br clear=right>

<p>

<a href="http://media.thetech.org">Visit the Media Lab Web server</a> for more info about programs for teachers and students.

