<!-- insert sidebar here -->
<p>
<a href="/hyper/tech10"><img src="/sidebars/TechTenSidebar.gif" border=0 alt="The Tech 10"></a>
<p>
The Tech proudly introduces the premiere issue of <a href="/hyper/tech10">The Tech 10</a>!

