</td>

<td valign=top width=75%>
<img src="MembershipAtTheTech.gif" alt="Membership At The Tech" border=0 width=397 height=57>

<p>

<h3>"Thank you for making your museum so exciting 
and full of wonderful things..."</h3>

<p>


<table cellspacing=5 cellpadding=2>
<tr>
<td valign=top><img src="PeterGilesSmall.gif" alt="Peter Giles" border=0 width=93></td>
<td valign=top>

December 1996<br>

<p>

Dear Friend of The Tech Museum,

<p>

Would you like to be part of one of the world's most exciting science and technology museums... a museum that is revolutionizing the idea of "interactive learning" and changing the very concept of what a museum can be?  Then you should be part of The Tech Museum of Innovation!

</td>
</tr>
</table>


<p>

You are invited to become a member of The Tech Museum and experience for yourself the fascinating world of science and technology.  

<p>

Only The Tech Museum can offer you the chance to discover the remarkable new advances taking place all around us. . . in space exploration, microelectronics, biotechnology, robotics, multimedia, and virtual reality, to name just a few!  And, as a leader in the development of  "interactive learning," the Tech's exciting, hands-on exhibits invite you to see, hear, touch, smell, and sometimes even taste today's newest technology!

<p>

From exhibits to workshops, special events to summer camps, The Tech is a place where you and your family can explore, learn, and have lots of fun visit after visit.

<p>

Membership is the best way to get "full value" out of every Tech Museum visit.  Starting at just $35 for one person, or $50 for the whole family, membership offers you an array of unique benefits designed to increase your enjoyment!  

<p>

What could be better than unlimited free admission, special discounts on programs and workshops, a 15% discount at The Tech Museum Store, a free subscription to the museum newsletter, and free admission to more than 199 science and technology museums around the country?!

<p>

And, as a special "Welcome to the Tech" bonus for joining at the $35 Individual level--you'll receive your own copy of "Science Experiments You Can Eat," a delightful pocket guide to edible experiments you and your kids can perform in your own kitchen!

<p>



<!--table cellspacing=5 cellpadding=2>
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<img src="KidsDoTheWeb.gif" alt="Kids do the Web book" border=0 width=200></td>
<td valign=top-->

<img src="KidsDoTheWeb.gif" alt="Kids do the Web book" border=0 width=200 align=left hspace=15>

As a double bonus for your $50 Family or Grandparent membership,  you'll receive both "Science Experiments You Can Eat" and "Kids do the Web," a colorful, graphics-filled "how-to" tour of more than 40 Web sites created by and for kids and teens.  

<p>

Additional, exclusive benefits are offered at the $100 Sustaining, $250 Patron, $500 Presidential, and $1,000 Entrepreneurial membership levels. A complete list of benefits is enclosed.  

<!--p>
</td>
</tr>
</table-->

<p>

Additional, exclusive benefits are offered at the $100 Sustaining, $250 Patron, $500 Presidential, and $1,000 Entrepreneurial membership levels. A complete list of benefits is enclosed.  

<p>

As an educational institution, The Tech is committed to inspiring a life-long interest in science and technology among people of all ages, especially young people.  To underscore this important goal, the museum's Board of Directors has made an extraordinary commitment to the museum. . .

<p>

Through December 31, the Board of Directors' Fund for Excellence will match your membership dollar for dollar, thereby doubling the value of your membership contribution.  Your $50 membership will be worth $100. . . your $100 membership becomes a $200 
contribution. . . your $500 tax-deductible membership is worth $1,000!

<p>

For this reason alone, there has never been a better time to accept our invitation to join The Tech Museum.  Your membership support will help us pursue our mission to engage people of all ages in the excitement of exploring today's technology while benefiting you and your family. 

<p>

Now, more than ever before, it's time to "Get into Technology!" and enjoy the benefits of membership at The Tech Museum!  

<p>

I hope to see you at the museum soon!  

<p><br>

Sincerely,

<p><br>

Peter B. Giles<br>
President and CEO

<p>

P.S. Remember, the Fund for Excellence will double the value of your membership if you join The Tech before December 31!  

<p>

P.P.S. Join now to reserve your copies of "Science Experiments You Can Eat" and "Kids do the Web," your double bonus for joining as a Family or Grandparent member today!

<p><br>

<h3>Basics Membership Benefits include:</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/astc.html">Free admission to over 199 science museums nationwide</a>
<li>Subscription to The Tech's newsletter Innovations
<li>Invitation to the annual Innovation Awards Dinner
<li>Discounts for special programs and workshops
<li>15% discount at <a href="/techstore.html">The Tech Museum Store</a>
<li>Unlimited <a href="/info/admission.html">free admission</a> to The Tech
<li>Membership card
</ul>

<h3>$35 Individual</h3>
<ul>
<li>Basic membership benefits for one person
</ul>

<h3>$50 Family/Grandparent</h3>
<ul>
<li>Basic membership benefits plus
<li>Free admission for parents and all children under 18
<li>Advance notice of Family Day events
<li>Special grandparent membership includes free admission for two grandparents and grandchildren
</ul>

<h3>$100 Sustaining</h3>
<ul>
<li>All above benefits plus
<li>VIP Pass: free admission for member and up to five friends
<li>Four Guest Passes
<li>Free gift from The Tech Museum Store ($10.00 retail value)
<li>Family Pass to the San Jose Art Museum and the Children's Discovery Museum (good for one visit for a family of five)
</ul>

<h3>$250 Patron</h3>
<ul>
<li>All above benefits plus
<li>Invitation to private Patron event
<li>Four additional Guest Passes
<li>Invitation to a private screening and reception at Silicon Graphics' Virtual Reality Visionarium
</ul>

<h3>$500 Presidential</h3>
<ul>
<li>All above benefits plus
<li>Invitation to private Presidential event
<li>Exclusive invitation to VIP hard hat tour of the new Tech (date to be announced)
</ul>

<h3>$1,000 Entrepreneurial</h3>
<ul>
<li>All above benefits plus
<li>Invitation to exclusive Leadership Circle event
<li>Invitations to INVENTING THE FUTURE events with senior executives and founders of companies
</ul>

