<h3>Explore the Future</h3>
Become a part of The Tech Museum of Innovation, where we inspire tomorrow's
innovators... today.
Experience technology in a user-friendly atmosphere.  Our hands-on,
<a href="/exhibits.html">interactive exhibits</a> get everyone involved.  Here you test and touch, play
and probe, design and discover the remarkable advances taking place in the
world around us.
At The Tech, your personal potential is unlimited, and so is your <a href="/admission.html#admission">admission</a>.
Join the Tech today!


<h3>Registration Form</h3>
Are you ready to become a member?  Use the <a href="signup.html">registration form</a> to signup now.

