<center>
<table>
<tr>
<td width=480>

<br>

<center><h3>The Tech Museum of Innovation Groundbreaking<br>June 11, 1996</h3></center>

<p>

"Over the past fourteen years, the staff of The Tech, the community leaders
of San Jose, and the technology leaders in the valley have put their heart
and souls, and the financial backing behind making this ground breaking day
for The Tech Museum of Innovation possible. As gratifying as this day is --
it is only the well deserved celebration of a new beginning.
<p>
The challenge ahead of us is to realize our goal of making The Tech the
premier world class example of an institution dedicated to education and
enlightenment of the wonders and possibilities that technology can bring.
<p>
We WILL excite young people about the possibilities of technology.
<p>
We WILL reach out to a global community with our messages.
<p>
We WILL achieve cooperation between industry, educational and civic
partners to make technology education a priority.
<p>
And we will have fun in the process."
<p>

<table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
<tr>
<td valign=bottom>
John Warnock<br>
CEO & Chairman, Adobe Systems<br>
Chairman, The Tech Museum of Innovation
</td>

<td width=100 valign=top>
<br>

<center><a href="park.html"><img src="/images/ui/arrows/smaller/arrow90.gif" width=33 height=33 alt="Next page.." border=0></a></center>
<p>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

<p>

<hr>

Read what the <a href="http://www.sjmercury.com/news/tech/">San Jose Mercury News</a> has to say about The New Tech.
</td>
</tr>
</table>

</center>


