408-279-7150 or send mail to <a href="mailto:info@thetech.org">info@thetech.org</a>.

<p>

<center>The Tech Museum of Innovation</center>
<center>145 West San Carlos Street</center>
<center>San Jose, CA, 95113, USA</center>
</td>

</tr>
</table>


