<br>

<center><h3><font size="+2">Founders for the New Tech</font></h3></center>

<p>Donors to The Tech Capital Campaign are ensuring the museum's vision
for expansion. We are deeply grateful for lead support as The Tech develops
exhibits and educational programs extending the facility by six times its
current size. </p>

<p><b>DISTINGUISHED FOUNDERS</b></p>

