<h2>Directions and Parking</h2>
The Tech is located at 145 West San Carlos Street in downtown San Jose, across
from the San Jose McEnery Convention Center and the Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. Main Library.  Convenient to Light Rail, bus and CalTrain.

<p>

The Tech is near Highways 280 and 87, and ample public parking is available nearby.  Limited free parking is available weekends only, and only at the River Park Tower building at Woz Way and San Carlos Street, two blocks west of The Tech.

<h3>Maps</h3>

Click the thumbnail images below for maps of San Jose and the Bay Area, courtesy of <a href="http://www.bigbook.com">BigBook, Inc</a>.

<p>

<center><table border=1>
<tr><td align=middle><a href="/info/street.gif"><img src="/info/street.gif" width=100></a></td> <td align=middle><a href="/info/state.gif"><img src="/info/state.gif" width=100></a></td></tr>
<tr><td align=middle><a href="/info/street.gif">Street map<br>of San Jose</a></td> <td align=middle><a href="/info/state.gif">Map of<br>Bay Area</a></td></tr>
</table></center>


<h3>Interstate 280 South(from San Francisco, Half Moon Bay, Stanford, Los Altos)</h3>

