<html>
<head>
<title>Special Events at The Tech</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<img src="/images/ui/redbar.gif" alt="" border=0>
<table cellpadding=2 cellspacing=10>
<tr>
  <td rowspan=2><a href="/"><img src="/testing/tlwtnew.gif" border=0></a></td>
  <td><font size=6>Special Events at The Tech</font></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td width=450><font size="+1">For a special event with imaginative conversation starters, bring your company or organization to The Tech.  The Tech gives your group an interesting place to meet, while finding out about the latest technologies through <a href="/exhibits.html">hands-on exhibits</a>.</font>
  </td>
</tr>
</table>
<img src="/images/ui/redbar.gif" alt="" border=0>
<h2>Availability</h2> 
The Tech is available for rentals Monday through Sunday between 6 pm
and midnight.  The facility is closed Thanksgiving Day, Christmas Eve
and Day, and New Year's Eve and Day.
<h2>Fees</h2>
The Tech rental fee reserves the entire facility, including the
Visitor Orientation Area, the
<a href="/exhibits/exhibit_hall.html">Exhibit Hall</a>,
<a href="/techstore.html">The Tech Museum Store</a>, and the Info Lounge.
The Interactive Media Lab and
Workbench are available for
demonstrations through special arrangement only.<p>
The cost is $10 per person up to 400 people for three hours, with a
minimum fee of $1,500.  After the first three hours an additional 30
percent of the original cost will be charged per hour.  Corporate
Affiliates of The Tech and non-profit organizations are entitled to
one annual 15 percent discount of the rental fee.
<h2>Deposit</h2>
To reserve an evening for your special event, a $750 deposit is
required.  The deposit is refundable if the event is officially
cancelled 30 days prior to the event.  The balance of the rental is
due within 30 days after the event.
<h2>Capacity</h2>
With approximately 15,000 square feet, The Tech will accommodate up to
400 people for an optimum experience in the facility.
<h2>Staffing</h2>
The renter is responsible for planning the special event, and The Tech
will provide the facility/exhibit staff, including an on-site
coordinator.
<h2>Catering</h2>
All food and beverage arrangements, including set-up, services and
clean-up are to be arranged by the renter exclusively with Service
America.  Contact their Catering Office at 408-277-5446 for menu and
price information.
For more information, contact Special Events at 408-279-7156, or
e-mail <a href="mailto:events@thetech.org">events@thetech.org</a>.
