<title>Exhibits at The Tech</title>
<h1>The Clean Room</h1>
A simulated clean room demonstrates how chips are made, from the pure
silicon chunks to a finished, packaged chip in a computer.<p>
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/exhibits/cleanroom-2.gif" alt="[For a digitized picture of
