<title>Exhibit at The Tech</title>
<h1>The Daily Living Robot</h1>
This industrial robot illustrates a new service application.  The
robot is a personalized assistant to a quadriplegic.  It responds to
voice commands from its user.  It is presented in a personal work
station and demonstrates, at the visitor's request, how it performs a
variety of services for its owner from answering the phone to making
lunch.  The display shows how a robot can help a disabled person be
more independent.<p>
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/exhibits/rehab-2.gif" alt="[For a digitized picture of
The Daily Living Robot, contact webmaster@thetech.org.]">
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/logos/tech/techbutton-footer.gif" alt="">
<address>The Daily Living Robot / The Tech /
<a href="/webmaster.html">webmaster@thetech.org</a></address>
