<title>Exhibits at The Tech</title>
<h1>The Working Robot</h1>
This exhibit demonstrates that a robot can be programmed to do
multiple tasks.  This robot does three different jobs including draw
the visitor's portrait, challenge the visitor to a contest, and
provide a quick demonstration of the automated assembly of a small fan
motor that works!<p>
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/fotoman/exhibits/adept_assembling_motor.gif" alt="[For a digitized picture of
The Working Robot, contact webmaster@thetech.org.]">
