<title>Exhibits at The Tech</title>
<h1>Alphabot: The Spelling Robot</h1>
This robot has a memory for letters and can spell just about name or
word you can give it.  Its computer memory stores the commands that
tell it what to do.  The visitor can type in a name or word for the
robot to spell out with children's blocks.<p>
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/exhibits/vanna-2.gif" alt="[For a digitized picture of
