<title>Exhibit at The Tech</title>
<h1>Space</h1>
Today's technology allows us to answer some of the biggest questions
that have been asked by astronomers for centuries.  We can look further
into space and back in time than ever before.  The Hubble Space
Telescope helps answer questions about the universe.  The Sample
Return Mission to Mars will tell us about Earth and about the
potential for life on other planets.<p>
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/exhibits/hubble-2.gif" alt="[For a digitized picture our model of the Hubble Space Telescope, contact webmaster@thetech.org.]">
<hr>
<img src="/gifs/logos/tech/techbutton-footer.gif" alt="">
<address>The Space Exhibit / The Tech /
<a href="/webmaster.html">webmaster@thetech.org</a></address>
