<h2>First Virtual Internet Payment System</h2>

<a href="http://www.fv.com/newacct"><img src="/gifs/fvmerchant.gif" hspace=15 align=left alt="First Virtual online financial transactions accepted here" border=0 width=75></a>

The Tech now accepts online financial transactions via the <a href="http://www.fv.com">First Virtual (TM)
Internet Payment System</a>.  This system allows you to make purchases and donations electronically and securely, without ever sending your credit card number
or other sensitive information over the Internet.

<br clear=left>

<p>

<h3>What to do:</h3>

<ol>
<li>Signup for a "VirtualPIN" from First Virtual's <a href="http://www.fv.com/newacct">new account</a> page, or by sending e-mail to <a href="mailto:apply@card.com">apply@card.com</a>.
<li>Go to the Web page displaying the Tech merchandise, program, or service you would like to purchase.  These pages are marked with the First Virtual logo.
<li>Complete the order form with your name, address, telephone number, and e-mail address so we can properly process your order or contact you in case an item is no longer available.
<li>Enter the "VirtualPIN" you received from First Virtual.
<li>Select or confirm the dollar amount to be transferred from your account
to The Tech.
<li>Press the <i>Submit</i> button to complete your order.
</ol>

<h3>What to expect:</h3>

<ul>
<li>First Virtual will send a confirmation message to your registered e-mail address.
<li>You can reply in one of three ways:  <b>Yes</b>, <b>No</b>, or <b>Fraud</b>.  See your First Virtual Terms and Conditions for complete details.
<li><b>Yes</b>: First Virtual will initiate the real-world transfer of funds from your credit card to The Tech, in the amount that you have authorized.
<li><b>No</b>: Your order will be cancelled without any penalty.
<li><b>Fraud</b>: <b>First Virtual will immediately cancel your account</b>!  <b>Do not reply Fraud unless you suspect that your
VirtualPIN has been used without your authorization</b>.
</ul>

Visit the <a href="/info/epurchase.html">Conducting Business with The Tech</a> page for a complete list
of products, programs and services available for electronic purchase from The Tech.

<p>

Also, feel free to e-mail us at <a href="mailto:info@thetech.org">info@thetech.org</a> if you have any questions.

<p>

Thank you!
<p>
Tech Staff

