We accept payment via the <a href="http://www.fv.com">First Virtual</a> (TM) Internet Payment System.
If you are not yet enrolled as a First Virtual buyer, we invite you to
<a HREF="http://www.fv.com/newacct/">enroll now</a>.
If you are ready to become a member of The Tech,
just fill in the following form
and send it in.
</td>
