<li>Virginia Living Museum: Newport News, VA
<li>Virginia Museum of Natural History: Martinsville, VA
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="WV">West Virginia</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Carnegie Hall: Lewisburg, WV
<li>Sunrise Museums, Inc.: Charleston, WV
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="WI">Wisconsin</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Discovery World, Museum of Science, Economics &amp; Technology: 
Milwaukee, WI
<li>Milwaukee Public Museum, Inc.: Milwaukee, WI
</ul>

<p>

Museums Outside the United States:

<p>
 
<h3><a name="argentina">Argentina</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Museo Participativo de Ciencias: Bueno Aires, Argentina
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="australia">Australia</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Scitech Discovery Centre: Perth, Western Australia
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="canada">Canada</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Discovery Centre: Halifax, Nova Scotia
<li>National Museum of Science and Technology: Ottawa, Ontario
<li>Ontario Science Center: Toronto, Ontario
<li>Science Centre/Centennial Planetarium: Calgary, Alberta
<li>Science World British Columbia: Vancouver, British Columbia
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="israel">Israel</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Bloomfield Science Museum/The Jerusalem Science Park: Jerusalem, Israel
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="philippines">Philippines</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Philippine Science Centrum: Manila, Philippines
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="singapore">Republic of Singapore</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Singapore Science Centre: Singapore, Republic of Singapore
</ul>
 
<h3><a name="sweden">Sweden</a></h3>
<ul>
<li>Teknikens Hus/House of Technology: Lulea, Sweden
</ul>

	  </td>
	</tr>
      </table>

