	    <!-- text cell -->
	    <h2>Admission to The Tech</h2>

The Tech is open Tuesday through Sunday from 10 AM to 5 PM.
Admission is $6 for adults, and $4 for youths, students and seniors.
Members and children 5 and under are free.

<p>

The Tech is a member of ASTC, the Association of Science and Technology Centers</a>.  ASTC members are entitled to free admission to many other museums through the <a href="astc.html">ASTC Reciprocal Free Admission Program</a>.

<p>

Call our Admissions Hotline at 408-279-7148, or our Group Info and Reservations Hotline at 408-279-7176 if you have any questions.

<p>

Please note that we are <b>closed</b> on the following days:

<ul>
<li>Mondays (except on holidays)
<li>New Year's Day
<li>Easter Sunday
<li>Thanksgiving Day
<li>Christmas Day
</ul>

