<title>Volunteer Application Form</title>
<h1>The Tech Museum of Innovation</h1>
<h1>Volunteer Application Form</h1>
<hr>
We like to hear from new volunteers.  If you are interested in
offering your services, please call us at
408-279-7150 to schedule an appointment.
<p>
<em>Note</em>:
If your browser doesn't let you edit the following fields, please send
your requests directly to volunteering@thetech.org.
<hr>
<h2>Name, Address, and Telephone</h2>
<form method="post" action="http:/cgi-bin/mail-volunteer-form.pl"><p>
Name  <input name="fullname"><p>
Address  <input name="street"><p>
City  <input name="city"><p>
State  <input name="state"><p>
<p>Zip  <input name="zip"><p>
Country  <input name="country"><p>
Home phone  <input name="nightphone"><p>
Work phone  <input name="dayphone"><p>
FAX  <input name="fax"><p>
E-mail address  <input name="email"><p>
Date of birth (optional)  <input name="birthdate"><p>
