	    <a href="/hr"><img src="/gifs/EmploymentOff.gif" width=121 height=16 alt="Employment" border=0></a><br>
	    <a href="/newhome"><img src="/gifs/NewHomeOff.gif" width=121 height=16 alt="New Home" border=0></a><br>
	    <a href="/feedback"><img src="/gifs/FeedbackOff.gif" width=121 height=16 alt="Feedback" border=0></a>



	    <p>
	      <!-- insert sidebar here -->
	      <p>
<a href="/revolutionaries"><img src="/sidebars/RevolutionariesSidebar.gif" border=0 alt="The Revolutionaries"></a>
<p>
Introducing <a href="/revolutionaries">The Revolutionaries</a>, presented by The Tech and the San Jose Mercury News.  This week's interview:  <a href="/revolutionaries/bushnell">Nolan Bushnell</a>.
	    <p>
	  </td>

