<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=5 width=400>
<tr><td colspan=2><h2>What's New at The Tech?</h2></td></tr>

<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/revolutionaries"><b>The Revolutionaries</b></a></td>
<td valign=top>
<a href="/revolutionaries"><img src="/revolutionaries/images/revlogo.gif" border=0 alt="The Revolutionaries" align=right></a>
The Tech and the San Jose Mercury News present <a href="/revolutionaries">The Revolutionaries</a>:  On Turning Inspiration into Innovation in Silicon Valley.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/hyper/tech10"><b>The Tech 10</b></a></td>
<td valign=top>
<a href="/hyper/tech10"><img src="/hyper/tech10/TechTenBadge.gif" alt="Tech 10" border=0 align=right></a>
Each month, The Tech selects and reviews our 10
favorite technology Web sites for teachers, students, and families.  Check out <a href="/hyper/tech10">this month's</a> edition!
</td>
</tr>


<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/info/fvips.html"><b>Online Purchase System</b></a></td>
<td valign=top>The Tech introduces support for secure online
financial transactions via the <a href="/info/fvips.html">First Virtual Internet Payment System</a>.  Sign up for <a href="/membership">Tech membership</a> without writing a check or using a postage stamp!
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/hr"><b>Employment Opportunities</b></a></td>
<td valign=top>The Tech offers competetive salary and excellent benefits.  Find out about the current <a href="/hr">employment opportunities</a> at The Tech.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/programs/challenge"><b>Tech Challenge '97</b></a></td>
<td valign=top>Signup to compete in <a href="/programs/challenge">Tech Challenge '97</a>, where you can land a robotic rover on Mars!
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td valign=top><a href="/techtalks"><b>Tech Talks '97</b></a></td>
