<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Mission of AEF</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY
BACKGROUND="backgrnd/vbar2.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#551A8B" ALINK="#0000FF" LEFTMARGIN="0" TOPMARGIN="0">
<P ALIGN="LEFT"><A HREF="index.html"><IMG
SRC="images/torcher2.gif" ALT="Return to AEF Home Page" ALIGN="TOP" BORDER="0" VSPACE="0" HSPACE="12" WIDTH="46" HEIGHT="59"></A>
<IMG
SRC="images/mission.gif" ALIGN="TOP" VSPACE="16" HSPACE="18" WIDTH="428" HEIGHT="42">
</P><P><IMG
SRC="backgrnd/spacer.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" VSPACE="1000" HSPACE="26" WIDTH="35" HEIGHT="4"></P><HR>
<P>
<H3 ALIGN="CENTER">Organizational Structure</H3>
<P>AEF is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization affiliated with the Air Force
Association.   Tax-deductible donations fund education programs and
scholarships.   AEF is a network comprised of a national office supporting AFA
members/chapters.  In the United States, there are 328 AFA chapters and another
23 chapters are located overseas. 
</P>
<P>AEF is governed by elected officers and a board of trustees and supported by
a small full-time staff
<BR></P>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER="1" ALIGN="CENTER" VALIGN="MIDDLE">
