<H2 ALIGN=center>Chapter Teacher of the Year Awards</H2>

AFA chapters are encouraged to select a local teacher for a Chapter Teacher of the Year Award
to honor an outstanding teacher who inspires an understanding of science and mathematics and
instills an awareness of aerospace technologies in their students.
<P>
The chapter can develop criteria to select a teacher suitable for the local area.  If your chapter
participates in the Regional Teacher of the Year Program, the chapter award may be an
excellent springboard for selecting a regional nominee. 
<P>

AEF will provide a Teacher of the Year certificate for use by the chapter.
<P>
Send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto: AEFStaff@aef.org">AEFStaff@aef.org</A>

