<IMG
SRC="images/afa_sup2.gif" ALIGN="TOP" BORDER="0" VSPACE="10" HSPACE="22" WIDTH="270" HEIGHT="54">
</P>
<P><IMG
SRC="backgrnd/spacer.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" VSPACE="1000" HSPACE="26" WIDTH="35" HEIGHT="4"></P><HR>
<H2 ALIGN=center> AFA Regional Teacher of the Year Awards</H2>


The Regional Teacher of the Year Awards was set up as a supplement to the national Christa
McAuliffe Award.  With so many dedicated and accomplished teachers competing for the
national award, AEF established a regional program to honor well deserving teachers.
<P>
The Regional award is run by the Regional Vice Presidents who establish criteria, nomination
deadlines, selection process and the presentation ceremonies.  AEF provides the awards, which
consist of a personalized AFA jacket, a $500 check and a certificate.
<P>
For more information about the regional award, contact your regional vice president.
