<TITLE>AF Junior ROTC Academic Excellence Award</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY
BACKGROUND="backgrnd/vbar2.gif" BGCOLOR="#C0C0C0" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#551A8B" ALINK="#0000FF" LEFTMARGIN="0" TOPMARGIN="0">
<P><A HREF="index.html"><IMG
SRC="images/torcher2.gif" ALT="Return to AEF Home Page" ALIGN="TOP" BORDER="0" VSPACE="0" HSPACE="12" WIDTH="46" HEIGHT="59"></A>
<IMG
SRC="images/resource.gif" ALIGN="TOP" VSPACE="16" HSPACE="6" WIDTH="430" HEIGHT="30">
</P>
<P><IMG
SRC="backgrnd/spacer.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" VSPACE="1000" HSPACE="26" WIDTH="35" HEIGHT="4"></P>
<HR>
        <H2 ALIGN=center>Air Force Junior ROTC Academic Excellence Award</H2>

AEF added a new dimension to its support of the AFJROTC program with the creation of the
Aerospace Education Foundation Vision Pin for academic excellence. The pin will be awarded to
AFJROTC cadets who maintain a 3.3 grade point average, and can be worn as permanent part of
their uniform.  
<P>
AFJROTC units can nominate cadets for the Vision Pin for Academic Excellence by sending
their names and GPA to the Aerospace Education Foundation at 1501Lee Highway, Arlington,
VA 22209-1198, 703-247-5800 or 800-727-3337, fax 703-247-5851, or email:
<A HREF="mailto: AEFStaff@aef.org">AEFStaff@aef.org</A>
<HR>
